gmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今日學校宣佈停課 <span style=\"color: red;\">隻支那狗又喺度玩嘢 話唔好停課 繼續讀書 另外又有隻支那狗對於今日停課一事表示開心</span> 完全唔知道今日之所以會停課嘅原因係因為尋晚有狗衝入中大攻擊學生 射TG 土瓜灣呢邊尋晚亦都射左TG 有手足更因為咁樣被捕 場面一片混亂  所以先至停課<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點對得住暴大學生 真係忍唔住開埋post屌鳩佢哋</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">各位千祈唔好亂打電話 人哋好窮㗎 換唔起電話卡</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"想繼續讀書又唔得，支持停課又唔得，媽呀好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nnds 都好多係手足，尋日暴大前線有幾個係 nds，將革命既種子輸入去大陸"},{"pid":"117ec5cef5e07430c338bc1a4915ab24a79de5b2","tid":1715454,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f55178b466f32bdb14cce2db37651ae405bf3d8","tid":1715454,"uid":292384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"你唔敢神獸佢就唔好阻住其他手足<br />\n又要遮名<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"68701bce29909e5bc4a70efb301f398313845f14","tid":1715454,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5957362b2d6e7b5426071d398ab25510bc2eb5c8","tid":1715454,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69f2676ffd9132041cd77be5df6408f20fc0772a","tid":1715454,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afghJsk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafghJsk.png&h=ec0df174&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrtPzy4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrtPzy4.png&h=369ee463&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c997md5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc997